\n< Serena >I can't attract attention. I have to
descend from somewhere else.

Serena> I don't have any business on the
rooftop.
\n< Serena >Alright, I can pass through a hole of this size.

\n< Serena >I wonder what's below... Mmm, I can hear
a voice.
\n< Serena >...Wait, I recognize this voice. This voice...!
